song.info:
From "Decycled" by Vectra, also called [url=http://bitworld.bitfellas.org/demo.php?id=7316]"Recycled"[/url]

"hai. i am louis armstrong or at least grade wants me to say so. excuses forever: i made this in four bloody afternoons. as a result i didn't have time to finish anything. (as you can bloody well see). enough for now: graffiti bridge calls period bai.
soli deo gloria"
